@startuml
title 外贸企业 AI 询盘转化与报价合规中台（二期）

skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 8
skinparam defaultFontName Microsoft YaHei
skinparam packageStyle rectangle

actor "海外客户" as Buyer
actor "外贸销售" as Sales
actor "销售主管" as Manager
actor "合规/单证人员" as Compliance

rectangle "海外触点" as Channels {
  [Email]
  [WhatsApp]
  [Alibaba / Made-in-China]
  [独立站表单]
  [LinkedIn / Facebook]
}

rectangle "外贸 AI 中台" as Platform {
  [消息接入适配器] as Inbound
  [询盘解析 Agent] as InquiryAgent
  [采购商画像 Agent] as BuyerAgent
  [报价助手 Agent] as QuoteAgent
  [合规提醒 Agent] as ComplianceAgent
  [跟进助手 Agent] as FollowAgent
  [人工确认队列] as Review
}

database "业务数据" as Data {
  [客户档案]
  [询盘记录]
  [报价草稿]
  [跟进记录]
}

database "外贸知识库 / RAG" as KB {
  [产品库]
  [报价规则库]
  [物流与贸易条款库]
  [合规认证库]
  [英文话术库]
  [客户案例库]
}

Buyer --> Channels : 发送询盘/补充需求
Channels --> Inbound : 统一入站消息

Inbound --> InquiryAgent : 原始询盘
InquiryAgent --> BuyerAgent : 需求字段\n产品/数量/国家/MOQ/交期
BuyerAgent --> Data : 更新客户档案\n意向分/买家类型/风险等级

InquiryAgent --> QuoteAgent : 报价所需字段
QuoteAgent --> KB : 查询产品/报价/物流规则
QuoteAgent --> Data : 生成报价草稿

InquiryAgent --> ComplianceAgent : 产品 + 目标国家
ComplianceAgent --> KB : 查询认证/出口限制/平台规则
ComplianceAgent --> Review : 输出合规提醒\n不确定项标记

BuyerAgent --> FollowAgent : 客户阶段 + 抗拒点
FollowAgent --> KB : 查询英文话术/案例
FollowAgent --> Review : 生成跟进邮件/WhatsApp 草稿

Review --> Sales : 待确认报价/回复草稿
Review --> Compliance : 待确认合规风险
Sales --> Buyer : 人工确认后发送
Manager --> Data : 查看转化漏斗\n高意向/流失风险/报价通过率

note right of QuoteAgent
AI 只生成报价草稿，
正式价格和贸易条款必须人工确认。
end note

note right of ComplianceAgent
AI 只做合规提示和资料整理，
不替代法律、报关、认证判断。
end note

@enduml
